de.gematik.ti.healthcardaccess.sanitychecker

Interface ISanityChecker<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of input to be checked. see check(Object)
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CmdDataChecker, EnumsValidationChecker, IntegerRangeChecker, ValueStateChecker

    public interface ISanityChecker<T>

    This interface defines how SanityCheck works. <br/> Firstly: CONFIGURE checker with setMsgIncaseError(String) and/or#setSpecifiedValues(Object…​) and/or #setSpecialConfigurationPair(Object, Object) and/or setCurrentParameter(Object). <br/> Then: RUN check(input) FINALLY clean the singleton-instance (see the impl-classes)
